    {
      "orgnr": "556035-5926",
      "company_name": "Aktiebolaget Cernelle.",
      "official_website_url": "https://cernelle.eu",
      "about_text": "Cernelle is the founder and leader in extracting pollen for medical use. Their products, Cernilton® and Cernitol®, contain Cernitin™ pollen extracts, which are active pharmaceutical ingredients. These extracts are used in the treatment of benign prostatic hyperplasia and chronic nonbacterial prostatitis. Cernitol® Novum has undergone over 40 clinical studies, making it the best-documented plant-based medicine for prostate problems.",
