      "company_name": "KAMI, Kalix Mekaniska Industrier Aktiebolag",
      "official_website_url": "https://kami.se",
      "about_text": "KAMI, founded in 1976 in Kalix, Sweden, manufactures high-quality profiled sheet metal roofs using proprietary pressing technology, offering up to 30 years warranty. Their renowned product, PLEGEL®, has established a strong position both nationally and internationally. KAMI's products are sold through resellers in the Nordic region and distributors worldwide.",
