      "company_name": "Ambulansproduktion i Sandviken AB",
      "official_website_url": "https://www.ambulansproduktion.se",
      "about_text": "Ambulansproduktion i Sandviken AB specializes in producing ambulances with a focus on safety and working environment. Their ambulances are designed in close collaboration with customers to meet high standards of safety and ergonomics. The vehicles are equipped to accommodate two forward-facing, securely seated passengers, providing a workspace where medical personnel can safely attend to patients during transit.",
