      "company_name": "Actil Warehouse Trucks AB",
      "official_website_url": "https://actil.se",
      "about_text": "Actil Warehouse Trucks AB supplies customers with warehouse trucks across Europe and other parts of the world. Their product range includes stackers, low lifters, and order pickers, all designed for efficient warehouse management. Actil emphasizes environmental responsibility, utilizing smart material choices and ensuring their properties are powered by renewable energy.",
