    {
      "orgnr": "556464-0497",
      "company_name": "Ventilationsprojekt i Nyköping AB",
      "official_website_url": "https://www.ventilationsprojekt.se",
      "about_text": "Ventilationsprojekt i Nyköping AB has been operating since 1993, offering services such as contracting, investigations, design, energy efficiency improvements, maintenance work in ventilation, heating, and cooling systems, service agreements, OVK inspections, installation and service of cooling systems, and building automation. The company operates in several locations, including Nyköping, Norrköping, Stockholm, Södertälje, Eskilstuna, Linköping, and Katrineholm. Their business idea is to create energy-efficient and healthy indoor climates, selecting the right technical content for each project to meet environmental and customer needs.",
