    {
      "orgnr": "556471-7477",
      "company_name": "TP Mur & Puts Aktiebolag",
      "official_website_url": "https://www.tpmurputs.se",
      "about_text": "TP Mur & Puts is a family-owned company with masonry knowledge passed down through generations. Currently run by the fourth generation, Simon and Andreas Patetsos, the company is renowned for its expertise in working with historically significant facades. Their skilled personnel possess extensive craftsmanship, enabling them to undertake all types of facade work. TP Mur & Puts has become an established name in the Greater Stockholm area, with clients including NCC, Skanska, and housing cooperatives.",
